:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMZN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMZN-US</a>)下跌1.29%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對穩健，賽富時(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRM-US</a>)上漲4.03%；美國運通(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AXP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AXP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AXP-US</a>)上漲2.52%；國際商業機器(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:IBM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/IBM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">IBM-US</a>)上漲1.88%；威士卡(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:V:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/V\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">V-US</a>)上漲1.19%；摩根大通銀行(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:JPM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/JPM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">JPM-US</a>)上漲0.93%。</p></section></main>",
