            "title": "盤中速報 - Workday公司(WDAY-US)大跌5.1%，報132.02美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Workday公司(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:WDAY:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/WDAY\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">WDAY-US</a>)截至台北時間27日22:30股價下跌7.09美元，報132.02美元，跌幅5.1%，成交量237,357（股），盤中最高價133.00美元、最低價132.02美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-1.08%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.81%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-1.18%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-3.19%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Workday公司(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:WDAY:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/WDAY\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">WDAY-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-4.91%</li> <li>近 1 月：-30.41%</li> <li>近 3 月：-38.17%</li> <li>近 6 月：-40.26%</li> <li>今年以來：-38.01%</li></ul></section></main>",
